videos.description: Ryan Agnew throws on target to TE Kahale Warring, who brings it in to give the Aztecs a 14-0 lead over the Wolf Pack.
videos.headline: SDSU doubles lead with 16-yard TD strike

videos.description: Toa Taua takes the screen pass and walks the tightrope down the right sideline, taking it all the way to cut SDSU's lead to 14-9.
videos.headline: Nevada RB tiptoes down sideline for 40-yard TD

videos.description: Ryan Agnew threads the needle to TE Kahale Warring, who makes a leaping grab and reaches for the goal line to make it 24-15 Aztecs.
videos.headline: SDSU TE makes 30-yard TD grab between 3 defenders

videos.description: Devonte Lee takes the direct snap and bursts across the goal line to cut the Aztecs' lead to 24-22.
videos.headline: Nevada trims lead with 2-yard wildcat run
